<SYNC Start=178946><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp; 
<SYNC Start=179325><P Class=ENCC> 
폴이 죽었대 
<SYNC Start=180441><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp; 
<SYNC Start=181388><P Class=ENCC> 
내가 도와줄 수도 있었는데 
<SYNC Start=182675><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp; 
<SYNC Start=183289><P Class=ENCC> 
폴 잘못이잖아 
<SYNC Start=184633><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp; 
<SYNC Start=185882><P Class=ENCC> 
그럴까? 
<SYNC Start=186914><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp; 
<SYNC Start=188402><P Class=ENCC> 
오늘 대체 왜 그래? 
<SYNC Start=189887><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp; 
<SYNC Start=190361><P Class=ENCC> 
